Translation: 一小部分人在接触某些光模式或闪烁图像时可能会出现癫痫发作或昏厥，即使他们没有癫痫或癫痫病史。<cf><cf>此游戏可能包含闪烁的灯光。<cf><cf>如果您可能易患光敏性癫痫，请在玩游戏前咨询医生。如果您出现头晕、视力改变、眼睛或肌肉抽搐、意识丧失、定向障碍或抽搐，请立即停止游戏并寻求医疗救助。<cf><cf>如果继续，即表示您已阅读并理解此警告。

纽约州普拉茨堡的名菜.这种光滑的肉酱经常被夹在蒸面包中的热狗上.

Translation: 这是一款标准的跑车轮胎.在柏油路面上性能出色,但在越野车中不太适用.使用合适的工具可以将其安装到车辆上.

Translation: 这是标准的冬季轮胎.非常适合在东北部暴风雪天气使用！使用合适的工具即可将其安装到车辆上.

source: A tiny bait & tackle shop built out of someone's garage.

Translation: 五星级食谱的小型收藏.

 电池使用时会耗电,但可以进行充电.

Translation: 毛巾可以用来擦拭身体.也可以用来擦拭地板上的血迹和污垢.

Translation: 用过的马桶刷.有点臭.触碰可能会引起疾病.

Translation: 这是一种方便的燃料,可用于生火或燃烧炉.也有可能在窑中进行精炼.

source: A utility cabinet marks an area as yours. Other players can't search nearby one, unlock locks, etc. unless you give them permission or they break it down. source: How burnt the food is. This will reduce quality and make you uncomfortable.

source: I think you need more metal for this.
Translation: 我认为这需要更多金属.

source: If locked, this item won't be transferred by "put all" or "take all".
Translation: 锁定后,该物品不会通过 '全部放下' 或 '全部拿走' 的方式传递.

source: If powered, charges batteries that are placed inside of it.
Translation: 如果已接通电源,请给内置电池充电.

source: If the firearm has no rounds in it, it can't be used. Load it by dragging ammo onto it or equipping it and reloading.

Translation: 如果此选项关闭,玩家将无法请求实用工具柜 (只能自行构建).

source: If this is off, vehicles can't damage players.
Translation: 如果此选项关闭,车辆将无法对玩家造成伤害.

source: If this is off, you won't rotate with your vehicle: you will look in the same direction.
Translation: 如果此功能关闭,则无法与车辆一起旋转,而是会看向相同的方向.

source: If this is on, containers that aren't owned by anyone respawn periodically.
Translation: 如果此设置处于开启状态,则会定期重新生成不属于任何人的容器.

source: If this is on, furniture like tables or chairs respawn periodically. Only has an effect in multiplayer.
Translation: 开启后,桌椅等家具会定期复活.该效果仅适用于多人游戏.

source: If this is on, hordes will spawn if you make too much noise, have a large base, etc.
Translation: 当这个功能开启时,如果噪音太大或基地太大,就会出现大群体.

source: If this is on, players can't claim utility cabinets, damage bases, etc. if the owners are offline.

source: If this is on, your camera smoothly faces the direction your vehicle is moving.

source: If this is set, people will need to enter a password to join.
Translation: 设置此选项后,必须输入密码才能加入.

source: If you had the balls, maybe you could take a shot.

source: If your utility cabinet contains more than a certain weight, it will consume significantly more resources.

source: Illustrated and captioned adventure magazine. Also known as a graphic novel.<cf><cf>Reduces stress.

带插图和说明的冒险杂志.也被称为图像小说.

 减轻压力.

source: In multiplayer, you can play remote videos on TVs. Turn this off to block them.

source: The one that started it all.<cf><cf>Put it in a TV to watch.

作为一切开始的作品.

 放到电视上去欣赏吧.

source: The only way to reduce stress is killing things.
Translation: 减轻压力的唯一方法就是杀死一些东西.

Translation: 该所有者可能是侦探,在线论坛主持人,或两者兼而有之.

source: The remains of the victim indicate they died from a fall.

source: The result of blunt injury. Should heal by itself.
Translation: 这是钝性外伤造成的.应该会自然痊愈.

source: The victim appears to be a victim of gastric rupture.
Translation: 受害者可能是胃破裂的受害者.

source: The victim appears to be a zombie.
Translation: 受害者看起来像个丧尸.

source: The victim appears to have been beaten to death.

source: The victim appears to have been crushed to death.

source: The victim appears to have been run over by a vehicle.
Translation: 受害者可能是被车撞死的.

source: The victim appears to have been run over by a very large vehicle, likely a train due to proximity to the tracks.
Translation: 受害者被认为是被非常大的车辆碾压,但由于距离铁轨较近,很可能是列车.

source: The victim appears to have bled out before losing consciousness and dying.
Translation: 被害者在失去意识死亡之前可能大量出血.

source: The victim appears to have drowned to death.

Translation: 被害人可能是窒息而死.

source: The victim died of a blunt impact.

source: The victim has many small lacerations on their corpse. It appears they bled to death.
Translation: 受害者遗体上有多处小型撕裂伤,可能是因大量出血而死亡.

source: The victim has multiple flesh wounds which appear to be from human hands.
Translation: 受害者身上有多处可能是人类造成的肉体伤痕.

source: The victim has multiple stab wounds on their corpse.

source: The victim is emaciated. It's likely they starved to death.
Translation: 受害者身体虚弱,很可能是饿死的.

source: The victim was bleeding from the mouth. It is likely they were poisoned.
Translation: 受害者口中流血.可能是被下毒了.

source: The victim's corpse appears to be dehydrated.
Translation: 受害者的遗体似乎出现了脱水症状.

You are playing the VEIN demo. Your stat levels are limited to 50.<cf>Buy the full game to remove this limit.
Translation: 您正在游玩VEIN演示版本。您的属性级别限制为50。<cf>购买完整游戏以取消此限制。

source: You are so incredibly stimulated your chest starts to hurt and tighten. Any more stimulation and you might have a heart attack.
Translation: 刺激过于强烈,以至于胸口疼痛,感到窒息.如果再给予更多刺激,可能会引发心脏病发作.

source: You are so stimulated it feels like your heart is pounding out of your chest. Might be a good time to take it easy.
Translation: 心脏受到的刺激几乎要跳出来了.也许是时候好好休息一下了.

source: You are soaked. Move to a dry area and use a towel or something similar.
Translation: 湿漉漉的.请移动到干燥的地方,使用毛巾等.

source: You are the original owner and can't leave.
Translation: 你是它原来的所有者,所以你不能离开它.

source: You are too tired to move this. Increase your Vitality to move things easier.
Translation: 移动这个太累了.如果提高体力,就能更容易地移动.
你正处于 LSD 的迷幻状态.

source: You are wearing something that blocks this from being worn.
Translation: 我身上穿着阻碍我穿戴它的东西.

source: You are wet. Move to a dry area.
Translation: 湿了.请移动到干燥的地方.

source: You ate something raw, rotten, or both.
Translation: 我吃了生的,腐烂的,或者两者都吃了.

source: You ate something satisfying and are content.
You ate something tasty and are content.
You ate something very satisfying and are happier.
You ate too much food and have a stomach ache.
You believed the zombie apocalypse was a hoax before it hit close to home.
Translation: 在丧尸大惨案发生在身边之前,我一直相信那只是我编造出来的.

source: You bit into canned food so hard you just died.
Translation: 因为用力咬了罐头而死亡.

source: You bit into frozen food so hard you just died.
Translation: 因为用力咀嚼冷冻食品而死亡.

source: You break this into a splint.
Translation: 把它劈开,做成一个支架.

source: You burned your hand touching material in a hot furnace.
Translation: 触碰热炉中的物质导致手部烧伤.

source: You burned your hand touching material in a hot kiln.
Translation: 我触碰了热窑中的材料,烫伤了手.

source: You burned your hand touching material in a hot kiln.
Translation: 我触碰了热窑中的材料,烫伤了手.

source: You can access the build menu by pressing B.
You can access the help menu by pressing F10.
You can become stuck in a sunken car due to water pressure. Don't drive into rivers!
Translation: 你可能会因水压被困在沉没的汽车里。不要开车进河里！

source: You can choose to start the game later than default.
Translation: 你可以选择比默认更晚开始游戏。

source: You can chop trees with any heavy cutting tool.
Translation: 你可以使用任何重型切割工具砍伐树木。

source: You can clean blood with a towel.
Translation: 你可以用毛巾清理血迹。

source: You can click on parts to see more information about them.<cf><cf>The <B>battery</> is dead. Let's see if we can find a new one in the garage.
Translation: 您可以单击零件以查看有关它们的更多信息。<cf><cf><B>电池</>没电了。让我们看看能不能在车库里找到一个新的。

source: You can copy this character's appearance data and paste it during character creation to clone this character.
Translation: 您可以通过复制该角色的外观数据,并在创建角色时将其粘贴,来复制该角色.

source: You can craft basic recipes here.<cf><cf>To craft more advanced items and weapons, you need to use a workbench, which you can build in the Construction Menu or find in the world.
Translation: 您可以在这里创建基本配方。<cf><cf>要创建更高级的物品和武器,您需要使用工作台.您可以在 '构建' 菜单中创建工作台,也可以在世界中找到它们.

source: You can dismantle furniture and items that normally require a powered cutting tool with a heavy cutting tool.
Translation: 通常需要电动切割工具的家具和物品,可以使用大型切割工具进行拆卸.

source: You can inspect a corpse and see how it died.
Translation: 可以检查尸体以确定死亡原因.

source: You can jump slightly higher than normal.
You can load 3 bullets at a time into a firearm magazine.
Translation: 枪支弹匣一次可装填三发子弹.

source: You can move 50% faster while crouching.
Translation: 在蹲伏状态下,移动速度可以提高 50%.

source: You can refill fluid containers at various fluid sources, such as rivers, gas pumps, and toilets.
Translation: 你可以在各种液体来源处给容器加注，例如河流、油泵和厕所。

source: You can reload magazines 1.3x as fast.
Translation: 你可以以 1.3 倍速度重新装填弹匣。

source: You can remove very hot things from forges, furnaces, stoves, etc. with no penalty with these equipped.
Translation: 装备这些时，你可以在不受惩罚的情况下从锻炉、熔炉、炉灶等处取出高温物品。

source: You can see exactly what treats a condition by checking your medical menu.
Translation: 你可以通过查看医疗菜单准确知道什么能治疗某种状况。

source: You can see how long it will take a compost bin to create soil as well as the quality of soil it will yield.
Translation: 了解在堆肥箱中制作土壤需要多长时间,以及可以制作出什么质量的土壤.

source: You can see it all from here.
You can see the exact health points of doors, fortifications, etc. and their weaknesses, if applicable.
Translation: 您可以查看准确的耐久度值,例如门或堡垒,以及任何适用的弱点.

source: You can select a difficulty preset below. This just sets presets for settings in the Advanced section below. Feel free to modify settings further there.
Translation: 您可以选择下面的难度预设.这将设置下面 '高级设置' 部分中设置的预设.如有必要,请进一步更改设置.

source: You can select up to 3 tag stats, but have selected fewer than 3.<cf><cf>They are free stat bonuses with no drawbacks.<cf><cf>Are you sure you want to continue without them?
Translation: 您最多可以选择三个特质，但选择的数量少于三个。<cf><cf>这些是免费的特质奖励，没有任何坏处。<cf><cf>你确定不使用这些特质奖励继续吗？

source: You can smell fluid containers to get an idea of whats inside.
Translation: 你可以闻液体容器的气味以判断其中内容物。

source: You can tell if a store's walk-in cooler is powered by the sound of its A/C.
Translation: 你可以通过商店冷藏室的空调声音判断其是否有电。

source: You can treat conditions directly from your medical menu, so long as you have the required items.
Translation: 你可以在医疗菜单中直接治疗状况，只要你拥有所需物品。

source: You can use debit cards at powered ATMs to withdraw money, if there is any money in the account.
Translation: 你可以在有电的自动取款机上使用借记卡取款（前提是账户中有钱）。

source: You can view all of your stats, their levels, perks, and XP progress in the stat menu.
Translation: 你可以在属性菜单中查看所有属性、等级、特性和经验进度。

source: You can't apply this - it is frozen.
Translation: 你不能应用此物——它已被冻结。

source: You can't attach a lock to a container while it's not in your inventory.
Translation: 你无法在容器不在你的物品栏时给它安装锁。

source: You can't build on top of this.
You can't change the lock on this - it is locked shut.
Translation: 你无法更换此物的锁——它已被锁死。

source: You can't change the lock on this. It is protected by a Utility Cabinet.
Translation: 你无法更换此物的锁。它受工具柜保护。

source: You can't connect this - it would create a loop.
Translation: 你无法连接此物——这样会产生循环。

source: You can't destroy your own seat.
Translation: 你无法摧毁你自己的座位。

source: You can't drink this - it is frozen.
Translation: 你不能喝这个——它已冻结。

source: You can't extract anything. It is frozen.
Translation: 你无法提取任何东西。它已冻结。

source: You can't get anything more from this.
Translation: 你无法从中获得更多东西。

source: You can't ignite anything with this. Make sure it is on, powered, burning, etc.
Translation: 你无法用这个点燃任何东西。确保它已开启、有电、在燃烧等。
你不能混合不同的气体。

source: You can't mix the fluid in this with the current contents.
Translation: 你不能将此容器内的液体与当前内容物混合。

source: You can't mix the fluid in this with the gas tank contents.
Translation: 你不能将此容器内的液体与燃气罐内的内容物混合。

source: You can't move this that far. Increase your Strength to move things farther.
Translation: 你不能移动这么远。提高你的**力量**以移动更远。

source: You can't pick this up - you're carrying too much already.
Translation: 你不能拾起这个——你已经携带过多物品。
你不能把那个放在这里。

source: You can't place this in the air.
Translation: 你不能把这个放在空中。

source: You can't pour anything into this.
Translation: 你不能向此倒入任何东西。

source: You can't put a lock on this. Locks can be attached to doors, containers, etc.
Translation: 你不能给这个上锁。锁可以装在门、容器等上面。

source: You can't put this away - there's no room.
Translation: 你不能把这个收起来——没有空间。

source: You can't remove the dirt as there are crops growing right now.
Translation: 你不能移除泥土，因为当前有作物在生长。

source: You can't seem to determine the cause of death.
You can't seem to keep a grip on anything.
Translation: 看来你什么都没掌握呢.

source: You can't smell anything. The syringe is too small.
Translation: 什么气味都没有.注射器太小了.

source: You can't transfer anything to a Utility Cabinet that it doesn't need for base upkeep.
You clear the glass with your {Weapon}.
Translation: 你用你的 {Weapon} 清除了玻璃。

source: You clear the glass, injuring your hands. Next time have something equipped or wear gloves.
Translation: 你清除了玻璃，伤到了手。下次请装备工具或戴上手套。

source: You clear the glass, protected by your {GlovesName}.
Translation: 你在 {GlovesName} 的保护下清除了玻璃。

source: You convinced people to give you their money.
You destroyed this but salvaged nothing.
Translation: 虽然破坏了这个,但什么也没救出来.

source: You died from a gunshot wound.
You died from a heart attack.
You died from a zombie bite.
You died from an animal bite.
You died from an arrow wound.
You died from ballin' too hard.
Translation: 他是因为太过努力而死的.

source: You died from being hit by a train.
You died from being hit by a vehicle.
You died from exiting a very fast vehicle and impacting the ground.
Translation: 你从高速行驶的车辆中冲出,坠地身亡.

source: You died from gastric rupture. Eat less next time.
Translation: 你是因胃破裂而死的吧.下次请少吃点.

source: You died from hyperhydration. Drink less next time.
Translation: 我因为水分过多而死了.下次请节制饮水.

source: You died from smashing into a wall.
You died in an unfortunate firework accident.
Translation: 你在一场不幸的烟花事故中丧生.

source: You dismantled this but salvaged nothing.
Translation: 我把它拆解了,但什么也没回收.

source: You dismantled this with your bare hands and received:<lf><lf>{Items}
Translation:
我徒手拆解了它,获得了以下道具:

{Items}

source: You dismantled this with your bare hands but salvaged nothing.
Translation: 你徒手拆解了它,但什么也没能回收.

source: You do some reading and feel calmer.
Translation: 读书能让心情平静下来.

source: You don't have a tire in your inventory to refill.
Translation: 你的库存中没有轮胎可以补充。

source: You don't have any clothes. Maybe you can find some dry ones in the bedroom.<cf><cf>Check the dresser with your <B>{UseKey}</>.
Translation: 你没有衣服。卧室里可能有干衣服。<cf><cf>按<B>{UseKey}</> 查看梳妆台.

source: You don't have any utility item equipped to use as a flashlight.
Translation: 你没有任何工具可以用作手电筒。

source: You don't have any utility item equipped to use as a map.
Translation: 你没有任何工具可以用作地图。

source: You don't have enough bullets to load this with.
Translation: 你没有足够的子弹来装这个。

source: You don't have the money for this. It requires ${MoneyInDollars}.
You don't have the required authentication to join.
Translation: 你缺少加入所需的身份核验。

source: You don't have the required skills to build this.
Translation: 你缺少制造这个所需的技能。

source: You don't have the required tool to dismantle this. You need {Tool} or a {Skill} level above {SkillLevel}.
Translation: 没有必要的工具来解构它.需要 {Tool} 或 {SkillLevel} 或更高的 {Skill} 级别.

source: You don't have the required tool to dismantle this. You need {Tool}.
Translation: 没有必要的工具来解构它.需要 {Tool}.

source: You don't know how much longer you can hold your breath.
Translation: 不知道能屏住呼吸多久.

source: You don't know what time it is right now.
Translation: 不知道现在是什么时间.

source: You drank some of the liquid.
You drank too much fluid and have a stomach ache.
Translation: 水分摄入过多导致胃痛.

source: You drank way too much and are experiencing alcohol poisoning.
Translation: 你喝得太多了,已经酒精中毒了.

source: You drink some of the contents.
You drink some of the toilet water.
You drink some of the toilet water.
You drink some of the toilet water.
You drink some of the toilet water.
You drink some of the water in the sink.
You drink some of the water sitting in the shower.
You drink some of the water sitting in the sink.
You drink some of the water sitting in the sink.
You drink some of the water sitting in the sink.
You drink some of the water sitting in the sink.
You drink some of the water sitting in the tub.
Translation: 我喝了一点浴缸里的水.

source: You dry yourself off a little.
You eat the food. Something's off...
You eat the food. You feel a little light-headed and drowsy.
Translation: 吃东西的时候会感到有点头晕,睡意袭来.

source: You educate children and teens about important topics such as math, science, and English.
Translation: 为儿童和青少年提供关于数学,科学和英语等重要主题的教育.

source: You emptied the oil from the engine.
Translation: 我从发动机里取出了机油.

source: You examine this and discover {Count} locations of interest nearby. They will now appear on maps.
Translation: 你检查了这个，并发现附近的｛Count｝个感兴趣的位置。它们现在将出现在地图上。

source: You examine this, but already recognize all of the locations it's referencing.
Translation: 你检查了这个，但已经识别出它所引用的所有位置。

source: You extract some fluid into the syringe.
Translation: 我从注射器中抽取了一些液体.

source: You extracted {Amount} of clean oil from the engine.
Translation: 你从发动机中提取了 {Amount} 的干净机油。

source: You extracted {Amount} of oil from the engine. It was dirty.
Translation: 你从发动机中提取了 {Amount} 的机油。它很脏。

source: You fail to hotwire the ignition, damaging the vehicle but protected by your {ClothingName}.
Translation: 你未接通点火开关，损坏了车辆，但受到 {ClothingName} 的保护。

source: You fail to hotwire the ignition, shocking yourself and damaging the vehicle.
Translation: 你没有点燃点火开关，让自己触电并损坏车辆。

source: You failed to connect to the server.
You feel a little drowsy and could use a nap. Find a bed or couch to use.
Translation: 你有点困了，可以小睡一会儿。去找张床或者沙发吧。

source: You feel a slight sting on your skin from a sunburn. Applying sunscreen will help prevent this.
Translation: 因为日晒,皮肤会有轻微的刺痛感.涂抹防晒霜可以预防这种情况.

source: You feel a strong burn in your muscles.
Translation: 肌肉会有强烈的灼烧感.

source: You feel a strong sting on your skin from a sunburn. Applying sunscreen will help prevent this.
Translation: 晒黑后皮肤会感到强烈的疼痛.涂抹防晒霜可以预防疼痛.

source: You feel a very painful sting on your skin from a sunburn. Applying sunscreen will help prevent this.
Translation: 晒黑后,皮肤会感到强烈的疼痛.涂抹防晒霜可以预防这种疼痛.

source: You feel extreme pain. Your skin is charred.
Translation: 感到剧烈的疼痛.皮肤被烧焦了.

source: You feel like your fingers are going to snap off.
You feel rested. Your respawn point has been set.
Translation: 你感觉完全休息好了。已设置响应点.

source: You feel strange, something isn't right...
Translation: 有种奇怪的感觉,有什么不对劲......

source: You fill the sink full of water.
You fill the sink full of water.
You fill the sink full of water.
You fill the sink full of water.
You fill the sink full of water.
You fill the tank with {Amount} of gas.
Translation: 给油箱加满 {Amount} mL 的汽油.

source: You fill the toilet bowl full of water.
You fill the toilet bowl full of water.
You fill the toilet full of water.
You fill the tub full of water.
You fill the tub full of water.
You fill the urinal full of water.
You fill up the tank. The tank is around {Percent}% full now.
Translation: 请将油箱装满.油箱目前约为 {Percent}%.

source: You gain XP for stats by doing things related to them, for example, running increases agility.
Translation: 你通过进行与各属性相关的行为来获得属性经验，例如跑步会增加灵巧。

source: You gave yourself a slight arm fracture and it's hard to use. A splint will help it heal faster.
Translation: 手臂轻微骨折,难以活动.使用夹板可以快速康复.

source: You gave yourself a slight leg fracture and it's hard to walk on. A splint will help it heal faster.
Translation: 脚轻微骨折,连走路都很困难.使用夹板的话会很快康复哦.

source: You get 30% less tired while sprinting.
Translation: 全力奔跑时,疲劳感会降低 30%.

source: You got a bit stressed from eating cooked food.
Translation: 吃加工食品让我感到有些压力.

source: You got a somewhat minor burn to your hand, akin to a sunburn.
Translation: 手上有像晒伤一样的轻微烧伤.

source: You got a very minor burn to your hand.
You got fourth-degree burns on your hand by touching molten material in a hot furnace.
Translation: 触碰到热炉中融化的物质,导致手第四次被烧伤.

source: You got great discounts at stores.
Translation: 你在店里得到了很大的折扣.

source: You got tangled in barbed wire and bled out.
Translation: 被带刺的铁丝缠住导致出血.
你收获了 {Quantity}{Quantity}|plural (one = 植物,other = 植物).你还回收了 {NumSeeds}{NumSeeds}|plural (one = 种子,other = 种子).

source: You harvest {Quantity} {Quantity}|plural(one=plant,other=plants). You didn't salvage any seeds.
Translation: {Quantity} {Quantity}| 收获了 plural (one = 植物,other = 植物).种子没有回收.

source: You have a 15% chance of receiving double the amount of items when crafting.
Translation: 在创建过程中,物品数量翻倍的概率为 15%.

source: You have a bullet embedded in you. Your mobility is limited and you are experiencing pain.
Translation: 子弹嵌入体内.动作受到限制,感到疼痛.

source: You have a chance of waking up in a random bed when you sleep.
Translation: 睡觉时可能会在随机床上醒来.

source: You have a dependence on a drug.
You have a fever. Due to it being viral, antibiotics won't be effective. You'll need to wait for this to pass on its own.
Translation: 你发烧了。因为是病毒性，抗生素无效。需要等待自行痊愈。

source: You have a fungal infection from walking barefoot. It smells pretty foul.
Translation: 你因赤脚行走而患上真菌感染，气味十分难闻。

source: You have a moderate arm fracture. A splint will help it heal faster.
Translation: 你有中度手臂骨折。夹板有助于加速愈合。

source: You have a moderate burn to your hand.
You have a moderate leg fracture. A splint will help it heal faster.
Translation: 你有中度腿部骨折。夹板有助于加速愈合。

source: You have a severe arm fracture. It's incredibly painful to use. A splint will help it heal faster.
Translation: 你有重度手臂骨折。使用时极为疼痛。夹板有助于加速愈合。

source: You have a severe fever and feel dreadful. Due to it being viral, antibiotics won't be effective. You'll need to wait for this to pass on its own.
Translation: 你有严重发烧，感觉极其难受。因为是病毒性，抗生素无效。需要等待自行痊愈。

source: You have a severe leg fracture. It's incredibly painful to walk on. A splint will help it heal faster.
Translation: 你有重度腿部骨折。行走时极为疼痛。夹板有助于加速愈合。

source: You have a very severe burn to your hand.
Translation: 你的手有非常严重的烧伤。

source: You have a {Name} that can treat this. Click the button to quick use.
Translation: 你有一个可用于治疗的 {Name}。点击按钮快速使用。

source: You have already read this. Reading it again will grant you XP but will not unlock anything new.
Translation: 你已经读过它了。再次阅读它将为您提供XP，但不会解锁任何新内容。

source: You have been granted permissions to build here.
You have built the maximum number of utility cabinets.
Translation: 你建造的储物柜已达到数量上限。

source: You have extremely high blood sugar and need insulin.
Translation: 你血糖极高，需要注射胰岛素。

source: You have extremely low blood sugar and need to eat soon.
Translation: 你血糖极低，需要尽快进食。

source: You have had too much exposure to the sun.
You have high blood sugar and are feeling dizzy.
You have high blood sugar and feel jittery.
You have ingested something toxic and feel kind of ill.
Translation: 你摄入了有毒物质，感觉有些不适。

source: You have injected something toxic into your veins.
Translation: 你将有毒物质注入了静脉。

source: You have invited them to your group.
Translation: 你已邀请他们加入你的队伍。

source: You have low blood sugar and feel lethargic.
Translation: 血糖值低,感觉无精打采.

source: You have no available utility slots. Unequip something first.
Translation: 你没有空位。请先取下装备。

source: You have no bullets to insert.
You have no bullets to load this with.
Translation: 你没有子弹可以安装这个。

source: You have no card to use.<lf><lf>Find them in the world and on corpses.
Translation: 你没有可使用的卡片。<lf><lf>在世界中和尸体上寻找。

source: You have no conditions. Lucky you!
Translation: 没有条件.真是太幸运了！

source: You're out of breath. Run speed and jump speed reduced; possible pain.
Translation: 你上气不接下气了。奔跑速度和跳跃速度降低；可能会感到疼痛。

source: You're playing the VEIN Demo. This area is available in the full game.
Translation: 你正在游玩VEIN 演示版。该区域在完整游戏中可游玩。

source: You're sleepy now. Time for a rest.
Translation: 你现在困了。休息时间到了。

source: You're sleepy. Find somewhere to lay your head to reduce this.
Translation: 好困啊.为了缓解睡意,请找个地方把头放下.

source: You're so filthly you'd make a zombie blush.
Translation: 你太脏了,连丧尸都会脸红吧.
负担太大了,感觉很痛苦.

source: You're so tired you could pass out at any minute. Find a bed or couch to use.
Translation: 我太累了,感觉随时都可能倒下.请找张床或沙发睡觉吧.

source: You're starting to carry too many things.
You're starting to feel thirsty and could use a small sip of water.
You're starting to feel very stoned.
Translation: 我感觉自己醉得相当厉害.

source: You're starting to feel woosy, you need to drink something very soon.
Translation: 我感觉越来越不舒服,必须马上喝点什么.

source: You're starting to smell and need to wash yourself soon.
Translation: 因为开始发臭了,所以需要立即清洗身体.

source: You're suffering from a moderately sprained ankle. It'll heal on its own, but all movement is painful.
Translation: 脚踝有轻微扭伤.我想自然会好的,但总之一动就会疼.

source: You're suffering from a severely sprained ankle. It'll heal on its own, but all movement is very painful.
Translation: 脚踝扭伤得很厉害呢.我想自然会好的,但总之动起来非常疼.

source: You're suffering from a slightly sprained ankle. It'll heal on its own, but all movement is painful.
Translation: 我轻微扭伤了脚踝.我想自然会好的,但动起来还是会疼.

source: You're suffering from dangerous withdrawl symptoms.
Translation: 你患有危险的戒断症状.

source: You're suffering from mild withdrawl symptoms.
Translation: 你正在遭受轻微的戒断症状.

source: You're suffering from moderate poisoning and feel ill.
Translation: 你正处于中度中毒状态,感觉很不舒服.

source: You're suffering from moderate withdrawl symptoms.
Translation: 你正在遭受中度戒断症状的困扰.

source: You're suffering from severe poisoning and feel very ill.
Translation: 你正处于严重的中毒状态,身体状况非常糟糕.

source: You're suffering from severe withdrawl symptoms.
Translation: 你正在遭受严重的戒断症状.

source: You're thirsty, now might be the time to drink something.
Translation: 口渴了,也许是时候喝点什么了.

source: You're tired and could use some rest. Find a bed or couch to use.
Translation: 我累了,想休息一下.我们去找张床或者沙发吧.

source: You're totally beat and don't feel like doing anything.
Translation: 完全筋疲力尽,什么也做不了.

source: You're very tired and could really use some rest. Find a bed or couch to use.
Translation: 我非常疲惫,需要休息一下.请找张床或沙发休息一下.

source: You've applied sunscreen to a decent portion of your body. You've reduced the chance of sunburns.
Translation: 我在身体相当大的范围内涂抹了防晒霜.这降低了晒伤的风险.

source: You've applied sunscreen to a small portion of your body. You've slightly reduced the chance of sunburns.
Translation: 我在身体的一小部分涂抹了防晒霜.这样稍微减少了晒伤的风险.

source: You've applied sunscreen to most of your body. You've moderately reduced the chance of sunburns.
Translation: 身体的大部分部位都涂抹了防晒霜.晒伤的风险适度降低.

source: You've been exposed to extreme heat or corrosion.
Translation: 可能会暴露在极度高烧和腐蚀中.

source: You've been invited to join {GroupName} by {PlayerName}. Press {Key} to view.
Translation: 您已被{PlayerName}邀请加入{GroupName}。按{Key}查看。

source: You've got perk points to spend. Spend these on perks to unlock them.
Translation: 您可以使用奖励积分.使用奖励积分来解锁奖励吧.

source: You've lathered yourself head-to-toe in sunscreen. You've greatly reduced the chance of sunburns.
Translation: 从头到脚涂满了防晒霜.大大降低了晒伤的风险.
电解质的平衡正在崩溃.

source: Your Femur is now located where your Fibula should be. A splint will help it heal faster.
Translation: 大腿骨位于腓骨应该在的位置.使用副骨可以更快地康复.

source: Your ability to break into locked doors or containers.
Translation: 破坏上锁的门和集装箱的能力.

source: Your ability to fix mechanical issues.
Your ability to plant, grow and raise crops.
Translation: 种植,培育和栽培作物的能力.

source: Your ability to take things apart.
Your blood type influences what happens when performing blood transfusions.
Translation: 血型会影响输血过程中发生的事情.
烧伤的程度是中等程度.

source: Your capacity to treat injury and illness.
Your cellphone has a flashlight! Equip a flashlight in a utility slot and press F to use it.
Translation: 你的手机有手电筒！在实用插槽中配备手电筒，然后按F键使用。

source: Your chances of becoming sick from eating raw meat are reduced by 50%.
Translation: 吃生肉可以减少 50% 的生病可能性.

source: Your chances of getting sick are tripled, and the effects are stronger, but you get a 5% XP bonus in every skill.
Translation: 生病的概率会增加三倍,效果也会更强,但所有技能都将获得 5% 的经验值加成.

source: Your character can't digest lactose-based foods.
Translation: 您的角色无法消化含乳糖的食物.

source: Your character can't smell anything (like fluids in containers).
Translation: 您的角色无法闻到任何东西 (例如容器中的液体).

source: Your character gets stressed from hurting animals and eating animal products.
Translation: 你的角色会因伤害动物或食用动物性食物而感到压力.

source: Your character gets stressed from hurting animals and eating meat.
Translation: 你的角色会因伤害动物或食用肉类而感到压力.

source: Your character has an insulin deficiency.
Translation: 你的角色是胰岛素缺乏症.

source: Your character is allergic to peanuts.
Your character's deleted when you die. Be careful.
Translation: 角色死亡后将被删除.请注意.

source: Your clothes are dirty. Find some new ones.<cf>Equip your new shirt by opening your inventory and dragging the shirt to the clothing slot at the center of your screen.
Translation: 你的衣服很脏。找一些新的。<cf>打开库存，将衬衫拖到屏幕中央的衣服槽中，穿上新衬衫。

source: Your compass HUD will show discovered & undiscovered locations.
Translation: 你的指南针HUD将显示已发现和未发现的位置。

source: Your creativity when combining unrelated items.
Translation: 组合不相关物品时的创造力.

source: Your emotions are blunted. Stress reduced.
Translation: 情绪会变得迟钝,压力也会减轻.

source: Your equipped {ItemName} has run out of battery charge.
Translation: 你装备的{ItemName}已耗尽电池电量。

source: Your family didn't vaccinate you. You are slightly likelier to get infected with the contagion, and can get rare diseases found in the world.
Translation: 由于您的家人没有接种疫苗,您感染传染病的风险略有增加,可能会患上世界上最罕见的疾病.

source: Your food poisoning is making you feel very nauseous.
Translation: 因为食物中毒的缘故,我的呕吐感变得很强烈.
冻伤的程度是中等程度.

source: Your game's version is different from the server's version. Make sure you're up to date.
Translation: 游戏版本与服务器版本不同.请确保您使用的是最新版本.

source: Your hands are nice and smooth. But why?
Translation: 你的手又漂亮又光滑.但是,这是为什么呢？

source: Your hands are starting to get oily.
Your hands are too slippery! Your weapon slipped.
Your hands are very oily, it's hard to keep things in your hands.
Translation: 手非常油腻，拿东西很困难。

source: Your heart is racing and you feel pretty good.
Translation: 你的心跳加速，感觉很好。

source: Your jump height decreases the more tired you become.
Translation: 你越累，你的跳跃高度就越低。
关于可移动部件的知识.

source: Your leg is broken. Find a splint in a medical cabinet. Its location is on your compass. Press tab to open your inventory. Click the Medical Splint and click Treat Injury.
Translation: 你的腿断了。在医疗柜里找一块夹板。它的位置在你的指南针上。按tab键打开您的库存。单击“医疗夹板”，然后单击“治疗损伤”。

source: Your max health is increased by 25%.
Your performance hitting targets with objects.
Translation: 使用物体攻击目标的性能.

source: Your persuasion towards getting good deals.
Translation: 你获得好交易的说服力.

source: Your report will appear visible to admins. They can then act on the problem.
Translation: 您的报告将向管理员公开,管理员可以处理这些问题.

source: Your save game failed to load. It's likely from a different version of VEIN.
Translation: 您的保存游戏加载失败。它可能来自不同版本的VEIN。

source: Your situation is not very Humerus. A splint will help it heal faster.
Translation: 你的情况与上臂骨损伤相去甚远.使用副木可以快速康复.
你的体力和有氧运动能力.

source: Your stomach aches due to something you ate.
Translation: 因为吃了什么东西而肚子疼.

source: Your stomach lining has started to tear and rupture.
Translation: 你的胃壁已经开始撕裂和破裂。

source: Your weight lifting capacity, melee damage, and knockback chance.
Translation: 重量提升能力，近距离攻击造成的伤害，击退的可能性。

source: Your {ItemName} broke because it got wet.
Translation: 你的{ItemName}已损坏，因为它湿了。

source: Your {ItemName} is broken, so you can't use it.
Translation: 你的{ItemName}已损坏，所以没法使用。

source: Your {ItemName} is broken, so you can't use it.
Translation: 你的{ItemName}已损坏，所以没法使用。

source: Your {ItemName} is missing parts to do this.
Translation: 你的{ItemName}缺少执行此操作的部件。

source: Your {ItemName} is out of power, so you can't use it. Replace the battery in your inventory.
Translation: 你的{ItemName}电量不足，因此无法使用，请在库存更换电池。

source: Your {ItemName} is out of power, so you can't use it. Replace the battery in your inventory.
Translation: 你的{ItemName}电量不足，因此无法使用，请在库存更换电池。

source: Your {ItemName} is turned off. Turn it on in your inventory.
Translation: 你的{ItemName}已关闭。请在库存中启动它。

source: Your {ItemName} is turned off. Turn it on in your inventory.
Translation: 你的{ItemName}已关闭。请在库存中启动它。

source: Your {ItemName} needs replacement parts to do this.
Translation: 你的{ItemName}需要更换零件才能完成此操作。

source: Your {ItemName}'s battery was drained because it got wet.
Translation: 你{ItemName}的电池因受潮而耗尽。

source: Zombie corpses won't go anywhere until cleaned up.
Translation: 丧尸尸体在清理前都会留在原地。

source: Zombies can break lights and windows.
Translation: 丧尸可以破坏灯和窗户。
丧尸只有被爆头才会死亡.

source: [DEPRECATED - NO LONGER USABLE]<cf><cf>Some chunks of limestone waiting to be recycled.<cf>Not terribly useful on it's own, but maybe in another form?<cf><cf>Used in advanced crafting recipes.
Translation: [已弃用 - 不再可用]<cf><cf>一些等待回收的石灰石块。<cf>单独并不太有用，但也许以另一种形式会派上用场？<cf><cf>用于高级合成配方。
{Count} {Count}|plural (one = 已装填弹匣,other = 已装填弹匣)
{Count} {Count} | 多个 (一个是撬锁器,另一个是撬锁器) 剩余

source: A blood bag. Can be used to extract yours or others blood for storage. Can also be used to transfuse blood to yourself or others.
Translation: 一个血袋。可用于提取您或他人的血液以供储存。也可用于给自己或他人输血。

source: A blood bag. Can be used to extract yours or others blood for storage. Can also be used to transfuse blood to yourself or others.<cf><cf>The universal donor, this blood can be used by anyone.
Translation: 一个血袋。可用于提取您或他人的血液以供储存。也可用于给自己或他人输血。<cf><cf>作为通用捐献者，任何人都可以使用这种血液。

source: A highly detailed blueprint explaining how to craft a new item.
Translation: 一份非常详细的蓝图，解释如何制作一个新项目。

source: Applies a temporary XP boost for 30 minutes.
Are you sure you want to dismantle this? It has writing on it.
Translation: 你确定要拆除这个吗？上面有文字。

source: Chop this with an axe to get usable logs.
Translation: 用斧头砍伐，可得到原木。

source: Dig this with a shovel to dig up remains.
Translation: 用铲子挖开此处以挖出遗骸。

source: Dig this with a shovel to to obtain glass shards.
Translation: 用铲子挖开此处以获得玻璃碎片。

source: Dig this with a shovel to to obtain metal scrap.
Translation: 用铲子挖开此处以获得金属废料。

source: Hit this with a pickaxe to get some ore.
Translation: 用鹤嘴镐挖掘，取得一些矿石。

source: VEIN is a passion project.<cf>It's developed for free.<cf><cf>We accept donations for server costs, but everything else is either from our own savings, or blood, sweat, and tears.<cf><cf>There are only 2 developers -<cf>one programmer and one level designer.<cf><cf>With that in mind, there are a lot of bugs right now, and many features are incomplete.<cf><cf>Please report bugs and feedback through the ESC menu ingame. We read everything.<cf><cf>Thank you for your understanding and enjoy!<cf><cf>— Kyle & Azi
Translation: VEIN 是一个热情之作。<cf>它是免费开发的。<cf><cf>我们接受用于服务器费用的捐赠，但其他一切要么来自我们的积蓄，要么来自血汗与泪水。<cf><cf>目前只有两名开发者 —<cf>一名程序员和一名关卡设计师。<cf><cf>考虑到这一点，目前存在许多错误，且许多功能尚未完成。<cf><cf>请通过游戏内的 ESC 菜单报告错误和反馈。我们会阅读所有内容。<cf><cf>感谢您的理解，祝您玩得愉快！<cf><cf>— Kyle & Azi

source: VEIN is an indie project in Early Access.<cf><cf>There are only 2 developers -<cf>one programmer and one level designer.<cf><cf>With that in mind, there are a lot of bugs right now, and many features are incomplete.<cf><cf>Please report bugs and feedback through the ESC menu ingame. We read everything.<cf><cf>Thank you for your understanding and enjoy!<cf><cf>— Kyle & Azi
Translation: VEIN 是一个抢先体验阶段的独立项目。<cf><cf>目前只有两名开发者 —<cf>一名程序员和一名关卡设计师。<cf><cf>考虑到这一点，目前存在许多错误，且许多功能尚未完成。<cf><cf>请通过游戏内的 ESC 菜单报告错误和反馈。我们会阅读所有内容。<cf><cf>感谢您的理解，祝您玩得愉快！<cf><cf>— Kyle & Azi

source: Immediately gain 2 levels in the stat.
Skill books give one extra stat level.
Translation: 学习技能书可额外获得1级

source: XP gained by related skill tasks is increased by 25%.
Translation: 相关技能任务获得的XP增加25%

source: You gain an additional perk point upon hitting level 100.
Translation: 达到100级后，你将获得额外的属性点

source: You learn a little bit more.
